room_title: Escape room "The Mobster's Speakeasy" by Time Trapped Escape Room in Tampa
review: Enjoyed this smaller place a lot! The 20s themed gangster speakeasy set was fun, and perfect for 2-4 people. Each problem was engaging and the quality of the room was very good. Good choice for a date; not the right choice for a bigger group.

room_title: Escape room "The Mobster's Speakeasy" by Time Trapped Escape Room in Tampa
review: Escaped from The Mobsters Speakeasy room for my birthday. So much fun! Kevin and Kristina were great! Look forward to checking out the other rooms at Time Trapped!

room_title: Escape room "The Mobster's Speakeasy" by Time Trapped Escape Room in Tampa
review: This was so much fun and such a great team building event! We had a team of 5 people and we achieved the 'escape' in about 46 minutes! What a sense of accomplishment! We can't wait to return to future themes with this great escape room business!
